title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode Two: Jagr, Young Talent, Bruins Captain
description:
After multiple aborted episodes, Rear Admiral and Ryan Whitney throw in the towel and hire an on-site producer. RA and Ryan talk about the young talent in the NHL, Jagr stories, if there should be a change in captaincy in Boston and much more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
